# TypeClear Support

Thanks for using TypeClear.

## Contact
If you need help, found a bug, or want to suggest a feature, contact:
- Email: mrrubikdev@gmail.com

## What to include in a support request
Please share:
- App version
- macOS/iOS/Android version
- Device model
- Steps to reproduce
- Expected behavior vs actual behavior
- Screenshots or screen recording (if possible)

## Common help topics
- Accessibility modes (low vision, dyslexia, high contrast)
- Voice features (TTS, captions, audio descriptions)
- Diagnostic sessions and adaptive training
- Progress export (CSV/JSON)
- TypeClear Pro purchase/restore

## Response time
We usually reply within 2â€“5 business days.

## Known limitations
Voice quality and available voices depend on the operating system voice engine and installed voices.

## Refunds and billing
In-app purchases are handled by Apple/Google stores. Refund requests must be processed through the store where the purchase was made.
